1
00:00:19,690 --> 00:00:26,890
♪Lights of swords are like
a splash of rivers♪

2
00:00:27,280 --> 00:00:34,320
♪Shadows of swords cover the seasons♪

3
00:00:34,700 --> 00:00:38,090
♪The clear water cuts off the gorge♪

4
00:00:38,910 --> 00:00:42,190
♪Which is facing the armed army♪

5
00:00:42,410 --> 00:00:45,780
♪Missing a pot of cold wine♪

6
00:00:46,520 --> 00:00:49,590
♪Drunk in the middle of sand♪

7
00:00:49,670 --> 00:00:53,520
♪The place of peace of mind
is my hometown♪

8
00:00:54,280 --> 00:00:57,240
♪But my hometown is by your side♪

9
00:00:57,240 --> 00:01:01,520
♪Who forgets about the grudges
in the past♪

10
00:01:01,830 --> 00:01:04,920
♪Don’t blame the west wind
for your tears♪

11
00:01:04,920 --> 00:01:08,700
♪To meet and to part are like a dream♪

12
00:01:09,430 --> 00:01:12,610
♪Well-armed with armor and weapons♪

13
00:01:12,610 --> 00:01:16,960
♪Where the surging river is going♪

14
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:22,960
♪Together we go to the end of the world♪

15
00:01:24,380 --> 00:01:29,980
=Legend of Fei=

16
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:32,940
=Episode 37=

17
00:01:43,760 --> 00:01:45,160
Miss Zhou.

18
00:01:45,590 --> 00:01:46,550
What are you doing?

19
00:01:48,950 --> 00:01:50,270
Are you lost again?

20
00:01:51,630 --> 00:01:53,880
I’m going
to get the Flaming Sage for you.

21
00:01:53,880 --> 00:01:55,390
Or how can I save you
with the Three-kind Decoction?

22
00:01:59,200 --> 00:02:00,670
Am I drunk?

23
00:02:08,160 --> 00:02:10,960
You roasted the fish poorly.

24
00:02:10,970 --> 00:02:12,380
♪Stars flow like river♪

25
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:14,160
This side has been roasted.

26
00:02:14,160 --> 00:02:15,400
But the other side is still raw.

27
00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:17,460
♪My yearning falls into the river♪

28
00:02:17,470 --> 00:02:18,470
How can you eat it?

29
00:02:19,640 --> 00:02:23,730
♪I dare not ask if you’re doing well♪

30
00:02:23,950 --> 00:02:27,760
♪The first time I’ve felt terrified♪

31
00:02:28,750 --> 00:02:31,890
♪Youth is like a sweet dream♪

32
00:02:31,910 --> 00:02:32,880
Fine.

33
00:02:33,630 --> 00:02:36,830
If you could stay when I was drunk,

34
00:02:37,070 --> 00:02:38,760
I’d like to be drunk.

35
00:02:38,760 --> 00:02:40,800
♪Now that you’re in my life♪

36
00:02:40,830 --> 00:02:42,070
When I get recovered,

37
00:02:42,710 --> 00:02:44,480
I’ll roast a delicious fish for you.

38
00:02:44,480 --> 00:02:45,910
♪I will never be alone♪

39
00:02:45,910 --> 00:02:50,130
♪I haven’t seen the mountains with you♪

40
00:02:50,350 --> 00:02:53,300
♪Nor have I tied up your hair♪

41
00:02:53,320 --> 00:02:54,470
When you wake up,

42
00:02:54,710 --> 00:02:56,490
the first thing I will do
is to punch you.

43
00:02:56,490 --> 00:02:57,780
♪We haven’t finished our story in chaos♪

44
00:02:57,800 --> 00:02:58,650
Why?

45
00:03:00,150 --> 00:03:03,750
♪The blade hasn’t been returned♪

46
00:03:03,760 --> 00:03:05,520
When you were little,

47
00:03:05,520 --> 00:03:07,470
Eunuch Wang bound you to the throne

48
00:03:07,470 --> 00:03:10,160
with his life.

49
00:03:10,880 --> 00:03:12,160
Your Junior Master

50
00:03:12,160 --> 00:03:13,990
kept you alive

51
00:03:13,990 --> 00:03:15,990
with all his force.

52
00:03:15,990 --> 00:03:17,950
♪I’m willing to shed blood for you♪

53
00:03:18,330 --> 00:03:22,520
♪Don’t mind whose land it is♪

54
00:03:22,540 --> 00:03:24,240
Now,

55
00:03:24,240 --> 00:03:27,200
you’re using the same trick on me, huh?

56
00:03:27,200 --> 00:03:30,820
♪Come and melt in my embrace♪

57
00:03:30,840 --> 00:03:32,530
It’s so clever of you.

58
00:03:33,350 --> 00:03:34,710
What do I do?

59
00:03:34,710 --> 00:03:39,320
♪The spring sun is an invisible armor
that’ll hold♪

60
00:03:40,070 --> 00:03:44,430
♪The purest love is unadorned♪

61
00:03:54,830 --> 00:03:56,190
Xie Yun.

62
00:03:57,320 --> 00:03:59,070
Wait for me.

63
00:04:19,440 --> 00:04:21,000
Junior Master Chen.

64
00:04:21,590 --> 00:04:22,680
Why do I feel

65
00:04:23,870 --> 00:04:25,240
the sun above Penglai Island this year

66
00:04:25,240 --> 00:04:26,720
isn’t as warm as before?

67
00:04:26,720 --> 00:04:27,750
Yeah.

68
00:04:28,190 --> 00:04:30,470
Before you get rid of Bone-chilling,

69
00:04:30,960 --> 00:04:33,520
you wouldn’t feel warm

70
00:04:33,520 --> 00:04:35,030
even if there were nine suns.

71
00:04:38,400 --> 00:04:39,840
You talk

72
00:04:39,840 --> 00:04:41,630
as directly as before.

73
00:04:42,750 --> 00:04:43,720
Xie Yun.

74
00:04:44,030 --> 00:04:45,470
Mind your words.

75
00:04:45,910 --> 00:04:47,590
You know what?

76
00:04:47,590 --> 00:04:48,840
I’ve got

77
00:04:48,840 --> 00:04:50,350
a present

78
00:04:50,350 --> 00:04:52,310
for Miss Zhou.

79
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:56,240
You still

80
00:04:56,240 --> 00:04:58,400
get to the point as ever.

81
00:05:03,070 --> 00:05:04,470
Speaking of Bone-chilling,

82
00:05:05,520 --> 00:05:07,120
when I was in a coma,

83
00:05:07,120 --> 00:05:08,800
I had a dream.

84
00:05:10,630 --> 00:05:11,560
In it,

85
00:05:11,560 --> 00:05:13,310
I saw many people I knew.

86
00:05:14,150 --> 00:05:15,590
Including Pathetic Clam,

87
00:05:15,590 --> 00:05:17,630
who invented Bone-chilling.

88
00:05:19,960 --> 00:05:21,470
It’s been years.

89
00:05:21,470 --> 00:05:23,590
It’s your first time to speak of her.

90
00:05:24,750 --> 00:05:25,720
Do you hate her?

91
00:05:27,350 --> 00:05:29,150
She’s just a borrowed weapon.

92
00:05:29,400 --> 00:05:30,870
When someone is hurt,

93
00:05:30,870 --> 00:05:33,280
he won’t waste time to hate a weapon.

94
00:05:35,150 --> 00:05:37,310
You suddenly bring her up.

95
00:05:38,240 --> 00:05:39,520
Is there anything on your mind?

96
00:05:40,910 --> 00:05:42,240
I’m just curious.

97
00:05:42,840 --> 00:05:44,720
After Shen Tianshu was defeated
in the Fortress of the Forty-Eight,

98
00:05:46,070 --> 00:05:47,560
could she still stay

99
00:05:48,240 --> 00:05:49,590
in Demons Manor?

100
00:06:01,960 --> 00:06:03,800
-Hyah!
-Hyah!

101
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:06,960
Weird.

102
00:06:06,960 --> 00:06:08,470
Why are there so many Demons?

103
00:06:09,350 --> 00:06:11,350
Since the token for
the Color of Ocean and Heaven appeared,

104
00:06:11,350 --> 00:06:13,150
the Demons are coming out
more frequently.

105
00:06:22,560 --> 00:06:25,310
I’m an off-staff disciple
with Qianzhong Sect.

106
00:06:25,310 --> 00:06:27,150
I come to take over the secret service.

107
00:06:27,150 --> 00:06:28,910
Greetings, Mr. Li.

108
00:06:29,750 --> 00:06:31,440
What are those Demons doing?

109
00:06:31,440 --> 00:06:33,750
They’re heading
for Cloud Ravine in the south.

110
00:06:34,310 --> 00:06:35,720
Looks like

111
00:06:35,720 --> 00:06:37,240
they’re after someone.

112
00:06:52,520 --> 00:06:53,240
Bonehead.

113
00:06:53,240 --> 00:06:54,750
Drink the water
and let’s get into the town.

114
00:06:59,910 --> 00:07:00,750
Someone is there?

115
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:03,680
A thief, I guess!

116
00:07:06,150 --> 00:07:07,520
He ran away so fast.

117
00:07:07,520 --> 00:07:08,680
He must be a spy,

118
00:07:08,680 --> 00:07:09,590
instead of a martial master.

119
00:07:09,590 --> 00:07:10,750
I must run after him, too!

120
00:07:10,750 --> 00:07:12,520
Or he will think I’m scared of him.

121
00:07:12,520 --> 00:07:13,280
Our priority is

122
00:07:13,280 --> 00:07:15,030
to deliver Flaming Sage to Lingling.

123
00:07:15,030 --> 00:07:16,120
Don’t ask for extra trouble.

124
00:07:17,870 --> 00:07:18,840
Fine, then.

125
00:07:19,440 --> 00:07:20,400
Let’s go.

126
00:07:21,960 --> 00:07:22,910
Wait.

127
00:07:23,520 --> 00:07:24,680
We won’t ride the horses.

128
00:07:24,680 --> 00:07:26,030
There’ll be loud tramping hoofs.

129
00:07:26,470 --> 00:07:27,840
Get the horses that way.

130
00:07:28,190 --> 00:07:29,310
We will walk.

131
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:32,070
You sound

132
00:07:32,070 --> 00:07:33,720
much more like your cousin.

133
00:07:33,720 --> 00:07:35,150
What’s the problem with that?

134
00:07:35,150 --> 00:07:37,350
We risked our lives
to get the Flaming Sage.

135
00:07:37,350 --> 00:07:38,070
If we lose it,

136
00:07:38,070 --> 00:07:39,400
we’ll be sorry to Ying Hecong!

137
00:07:39,400 --> 00:07:40,240
Hurry!

138
00:07:40,240 --> 00:07:41,070
Okay.

139
00:07:55,870 --> 00:07:57,030
Have we got rid of them?

140
00:07:57,030 --> 00:07:59,070
They must have followed the horses

141
00:07:59,070 --> 00:08:00,840
and won’t come back.

142
00:08:00,840 --> 00:08:01,660
Let’s go.

143
00:08:04,590 --> 00:08:05,870
Someone is here.

144
00:08:09,030 --> 00:08:10,680
Sheng?

145
00:08:11,120 --> 00:08:13,000
Why is it you?

146
00:08:14,560 --> 00:08:16,000
Oh, Li Sheng!

147
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:17,680
Finally, you’ve come!

148
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:18,520
At last, I can give her to you

149
00:08:18,520 --> 00:08:20,280
without any wound!

150
00:08:20,280 --> 00:08:22,280
We had such a hard trip.

151
00:08:22,960 --> 00:08:24,520
So hard!

152
00:08:24,800 --> 00:08:25,910
Sheng, you have no idea.

153
00:08:25,910 --> 00:08:27,840
I asked you to go back home, didn’t I?

154
00:08:27,840 --> 00:08:29,720
Why did you mess up with the Demons?

155
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:30,800
If you don’t
practice martial arts carefully,

156
00:08:30,800 --> 00:08:32,590
you will regret!

157
00:08:32,590 --> 00:08:34,200
Didn’t Aunt say so?

158
00:08:34,200 --> 00:08:35,200
Didn’t I say so?

159
00:08:35,200 --> 00:08:36,470
You have good luck today.

160
00:08:36,470 --> 00:08:38,200
But can you have good luck every day?

161
00:08:38,200 --> 00:08:39,910
Can you have good luck all your life?

162
00:08:39,910 --> 00:08:41,000
Li Sheng.

163
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:42,910
Yan suffered quite a lot.

164
00:08:42,910 --> 00:08:44,470
Stop complaining about her.

165
00:08:45,320 --> 00:08:46,240
Yeah.

166
00:08:46,240 --> 00:08:47,200
Yeah.

167
00:08:47,200 --> 00:08:49,150
She saved our sect.

168
00:08:49,150 --> 00:08:51,120
She isn’t that weak.

169
00:08:51,390 --> 00:08:52,470
You have such good luck?

170
00:08:56,830 --> 00:08:57,830
Thank you, Mr. Yang.

171
00:08:57,830 --> 00:08:59,240
My sister always makes trouble.

172
00:08:59,350 --> 00:09:00,710
Sorry to have bothered you.

173
00:09:01,120 --> 00:09:02,800
It... It doesn’t matter.

174
00:09:04,440 --> 00:09:05,640
Oh,

175
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:06,830
what about the medicine

176
00:09:06,830 --> 00:09:08,590
you looked for Fei?

177
00:09:12,640 --> 00:09:14,120
Here.

178
00:09:15,830 --> 00:09:17,350
This is precious.

179
00:09:17,350 --> 00:09:18,880
We must give it to Fei right away.

180
00:09:23,320 --> 00:09:24,440
Hyah!

181
00:09:24,830 --> 00:09:25,950
Hyah!

182
00:09:27,270 --> 00:09:28,390
Hyah!

183
00:09:33,270 --> 00:09:35,800
A timely arrival is better
than an early one.

184
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:38,270
You’re all here.

185
00:09:43,080 --> 00:09:44,150
Chuchu.

186
00:09:44,150 --> 00:09:45,910
Take Yan to find Fei.

187
00:09:45,910 --> 00:09:47,080
We’ll stop him.

188
00:09:47,080 --> 00:09:48,030
Okay.

189
00:09:50,270 --> 00:09:52,150
Yan, let’s go.

190
00:09:52,800 --> 00:09:53,950
Wanna run away?

191
00:09:53,950 --> 00:09:54,830
Don’t run after them.

192
00:09:55,950 --> 00:09:57,830
They’re not who Lord wants.

193
00:09:57,830 --> 00:09:59,350
Don’t waste our time.

194
00:10:01,680 --> 00:10:02,910
Li Sheng.

195
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:06,120
I know you have the Flaming Sage.

196
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:09,640
Give it to me.

197
00:10:10,760 --> 00:10:12,080
Give it to me!

198
00:10:21,120 --> 00:10:22,240
Shoot it.

199
00:10:34,590 --> 00:10:35,800
Take them down.

200
00:10:38,470 --> 00:10:40,680
Yan, we have to count on you.

201
00:10:40,680 --> 00:10:43,030
Chuchu, I can just do poses.

202
00:10:43,710 --> 00:10:45,150
You should have told me earlier.

203
00:10:45,150 --> 00:10:46,390
What do we do, then?

204
00:10:46,390 --> 00:10:47,760
Do you think we can convince them?

205
00:10:47,760 --> 00:10:48,950
Let me do it.

206
00:10:48,950 --> 00:10:50,080
Hold your breath.

207
00:11:08,440 --> 00:11:09,560
Hurry!

208
00:11:12,440 --> 00:11:13,560
Yan.

209
00:11:13,910 --> 00:11:14,910
Chuchu.

210
00:11:14,910 --> 00:11:16,270
What powder did you use?

211
00:11:16,270 --> 00:11:18,030
It wasn’t powder, but flour.

212
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:20,080
Go!

213
00:11:36,470 --> 00:11:37,510
Li Sheng.

214
00:11:37,760 --> 00:11:39,560
Did you send the signal

215
00:11:39,560 --> 00:11:41,320
because you knew
I was just on my way to the south?

216
00:11:41,640 --> 00:11:43,080
I didn’t!

217
00:11:43,080 --> 00:11:44,950
I didn’t know you could come so quickly.

218
00:11:45,760 --> 00:11:46,910
Where is the Flaming Sage?

219
00:11:52,800 --> 00:11:53,760
Where are Li Yan and Chuchu?

220
00:11:53,760 --> 00:11:54,910
They left before us.

221
00:11:58,910 --> 00:12:00,880
Chuchu, I’m too tired to run.

222
00:12:04,830 --> 00:12:06,080
Hold your breath.

223
00:12:07,830 --> 00:12:09,350
This is true powder.

224
00:12:09,760 --> 00:12:10,880
Are you using the same trick

225
00:12:10,880 --> 00:12:12,270
to sprinkle some flour?

226
00:12:12,270 --> 00:12:13,880
Do you think
we’ll fall into the trick again?

227
00:12:13,880 --> 00:12:14,680
Go!

228
00:12:15,030 --> 00:12:16,270
Go!

229
00:12:20,390 --> 00:12:21,200
Chuchu.

230
00:12:21,200 --> 00:12:22,710
What was that?

231
00:12:22,710 --> 00:12:24,560
The sleeping drug your brother gave me.

232
00:12:25,390 --> 00:12:26,760
So,

233
00:12:27,710 --> 00:12:30,120
you’re Zhou Fei,
the heiress of the South Blade

234
00:12:30,120 --> 00:12:32,470
my Lord mentioned?

235
00:12:32,470 --> 00:12:33,830
Lord Tong.

236
00:12:33,830 --> 00:12:35,510
Long time no see.

237
00:12:35,510 --> 00:12:37,350
You still look strong.

238
00:12:37,350 --> 00:12:39,080
Why are you greeting each other?

239
00:12:39,080 --> 00:12:40,350
We should, of course.

240
00:12:40,510 --> 00:12:43,120
Lord Tong and I are destined to meet.

241
00:12:43,120 --> 00:12:44,830
We’re also old acquaintances.

242
00:12:44,830 --> 00:12:46,240
When I was little,

243
00:12:46,240 --> 00:12:47,470
he tried to snatch the Bracelet from me
in the Fortress of the Forty-Eight.

244
00:12:47,470 --> 00:12:49,390
I poked one of his eyes.

245
00:12:49,950 --> 00:12:51,030
Lord Tong.

246
00:12:51,320 --> 00:12:53,270
For the sake of our acquaintance,

247
00:12:53,470 --> 00:12:55,390
please turn a blind eye

248
00:12:55,390 --> 00:12:57,640
if my cousin has offended you.

249
00:12:58,000 --> 00:13:00,240
I’ll pay you with the other eye.

250
00:13:00,560 --> 00:13:02,030
Very well.

251
00:13:02,030 --> 00:13:03,640
Chuchu and Li Yan may be in danger.

252
00:13:03,950 --> 00:13:05,270
Go help them.

253
00:13:05,270 --> 00:13:06,470
I’ll hold him back.

254
00:13:06,880 --> 00:13:07,950
No way.

255
00:13:08,350 --> 00:13:09,560
He can turn a blind eye,

256
00:13:09,560 --> 00:13:10,200
but I can’t!

257
00:13:10,200 --> 00:13:11,000
He’s my enemy!

258
00:13:11,000 --> 00:13:12,470
So,

259
00:13:13,080 --> 00:13:14,560
he’s your cousin?

260
00:13:14,760 --> 00:13:15,880
Go.

261
00:13:15,880 --> 00:13:17,150
Can you handle him alone?

262
00:13:17,150 --> 00:13:18,680
He’s a mere Demon.

263
00:13:19,080 --> 00:13:20,030
Just go.

264
00:13:20,440 --> 00:13:22,000
Lord Tong, the other day,

265
00:13:22,000 --> 00:13:24,510
Lord Lu tried to snatch
a Fire Lotus from me.

266
00:13:24,510 --> 00:13:27,390
Now you want
to snatch the Flaming Sage from me.

267
00:13:27,390 --> 00:13:28,150
Why do you people

268
00:13:28,150 --> 00:13:29,830
always want medicinal materials?

269
00:13:30,030 --> 00:13:31,830
Shame on you.

270
00:13:32,120 --> 00:13:34,390
Does Lord Shen want to run a pharmacy?

271
00:13:34,950 --> 00:13:36,880
How arrogant you sound!

272
00:13:37,030 --> 00:13:38,680
My Lord wants

273
00:13:38,680 --> 00:13:40,270
to exchange the Flaming Sage

274
00:13:40,270 --> 00:13:42,760
for the Seal of Cautiousness!

275
00:13:45,320 --> 00:13:47,270
You’re not too stupid.

276
00:13:47,270 --> 00:13:49,760
Unfortunately, I don’t have the Seal.

277
00:13:50,320 --> 00:13:51,910
You can’t get it even if you kill me.

278
00:13:51,910 --> 00:13:54,080
Not to mention you can’t kill me.

279
00:13:54,080 --> 00:13:56,080
Think about it carefully.

280
00:13:56,470 --> 00:13:58,390
Lord, Mr. Shen received a secret letter.

281
00:13:58,390 --> 00:14:00,760
Phoenix Master had
the Seal of Cautiousness.

282
00:14:04,590 --> 00:14:05,910
Very well.

