How does it sound? Stick to the topic?

565
00:31:16,600 --> 00:31:19,910
It’s so optimistic of you.

566
00:31:19,910 --> 00:31:22,480
Seems like you’re not dying.

567
00:31:23,600 --> 00:31:24,840
Now,

568
00:31:24,840 --> 00:31:28,080
I’ve experienced that life is short.

569
00:31:33,040 --> 00:31:34,720
♪Misty smoke blurs my eyes♪

570
00:31:34,720 --> 00:31:36,720
If I wear such a red dress,

571
00:31:36,720 --> 00:31:38,630
I will look beautiful, too.

572
00:31:39,150 --> 00:31:41,320
This fairy in the picture is...

573
00:31:42,110 --> 00:31:42,960
Guess.

574
00:31:42,960 --> 00:31:43,850
♪The blowing wind♪

575
00:31:43,870 --> 00:31:45,230
Guess?

576
00:31:45,230 --> 00:31:46,920
♪Frost and snow fall by the window♪

577
00:31:46,940 --> 00:31:48,990
It’s the name of the painting?

578
00:31:48,990 --> 00:31:50,680
You’re wrong.

579
00:31:50,680 --> 00:31:53,040
This is my wife.

580
00:31:54,230 --> 00:31:58,870
(This is my wife.)
♪Warhorses race on the turbulent cloud♪

581
00:31:59,350 --> 00:32:03,130
♪Guard the lucid water♪

582
00:32:03,620 --> 00:32:07,200
♪Chaos is the last thing I want♪

583
00:32:07,320 --> 00:32:08,800
Fei.

584
00:32:08,800 --> 00:32:11,870
There’s much sea food by the East Sea.

585
00:32:11,870 --> 00:32:14,390
It’s of the same race of you.

586
00:32:14,390 --> 00:32:17,150
With all kinds of seasoning,

587
00:32:17,150 --> 00:32:18,960
it will taste great.

588
00:32:18,960 --> 00:32:21,510
You can get familiar with it.

589
00:32:23,110 --> 00:32:26,480
The brush and ink are ready on the desk.

590
00:32:26,480 --> 00:32:28,270
Please show some mercy.

591
00:32:28,270 --> 00:32:30,200
A long letter will be better.

592
00:32:30,200 --> 00:32:32,080
A short letter will be good, too.

593
00:32:32,080 --> 00:32:33,390
Please write something in reply

594
00:32:33,390 --> 00:32:36,210
to relieve me of lovesickness.

595
00:32:37,320 --> 00:32:39,270
Oh, by the way,

596
00:32:39,270 --> 00:32:42,120
you can only use
the brush and ink on paper.

597
00:32:42,800 --> 00:32:44,270
Don’t use them on anything else.

598
00:32:46,040 --> 00:32:48,630
♪Red dress makes me enchanted♪

599
00:32:48,630 --> 00:32:50,940
♪Plenty of memories followed♪

600
00:32:50,940 --> 00:32:53,090
♪You were brandishing broadsword
at first sight♪

601
00:32:53,100 --> 00:32:54,850
I didn’t know what to write.

602
00:32:55,630 --> 00:32:57,780
But you enlightened me.

603
00:32:58,270 --> 00:33:00,280
You asked for this.

604
00:33:00,280 --> 00:33:04,590
♪Ever hid the worries♪

605
00:33:04,590 --> 00:33:06,850
♪No dim light at dawn♪

606
00:33:07,040 --> 00:33:09,240
♪Candles in still♪

607
00:33:09,370 --> 00:33:13,710
♪But right to shade your beauty♪

608
00:33:13,960 --> 00:33:16,660
♪It has three kinds of life-saver♪

609
00:33:16,660 --> 00:33:19,170
♪If I cannot wait for your back♪

610
00:33:19,170 --> 00:33:22,360
♪Hope I can still love you
20 years later♪

611
00:33:22,700 --> 00:33:26,170
♪I won’t be regretful♪

612
00:33:42,330 --> 00:33:44,710
♪The black hair falls down♪

613
00:33:45,060 --> 00:33:48,300
♪The good-looking face♪

614
00:33:51,530 --> 00:33:53,890
♪Is pure enough♪

615
00:33:54,340 --> 00:33:57,940
♪But push away cloud palm for you♪

616
00:34:00,770 --> 00:34:03,110
(Wang)
♪Live on remaining year sin degradation♪

617
00:34:03,610 --> 00:34:08,010
♪It’s just I thought♪

618
00:34:09,160 --> 00:34:12,580
♪Now I am sealed by love♪

619
00:34:12,580 --> 00:34:16,960
♪Only want to see you more times♪

620
00:34:18,370 --> 00:34:20,920
♪Red dress makes me enchanted♪

621
00:34:20,920 --> 00:34:23,260
♪Plenty of memories followed♪

622
00:34:23,260 --> 00:34:27,320
♪You were brandishing broadsword
at first sight♪

623
00:34:27,640 --> 00:34:29,940
♪The youth not know retreat♪

624
00:34:30,130 --> 00:34:32,270
♪Who is to be favored by fate♪

625
00:34:32,520 --> 00:34:36,840
♪Ever hid the worries♪

626
00:34:36,840 --> 00:34:39,380
(I’ll punch you.)
♪No dim light at dawn♪

627
00:34:39,380 --> 00:34:41,770
♪Candles in still♪

628
00:34:41,770 --> 00:34:46,200
♪But right to shade your beauty♪

629
00:34:46,200 --> 00:34:48,980
♪It has three kinds of life-saver♪

630
00:34:48,980 --> 00:34:51,470
♪If I cannot wait for your back♪

631
00:34:51,470 --> 00:34:55,010
(I’ll punch you.)
♪Hope I can still love you♪

632
00:34:55,010 --> 00:34:58,580
♪I won’t be regretful♪

633
00:35:03,640 --> 00:35:05,800
This place is as hot as a stove.

634
00:35:07,080 --> 00:35:09,670
But your hands are as cold as ice.

635
00:35:18,380 --> 00:35:21,100
(Wang)

636
00:35:54,640 --> 00:35:56,840
When there’s even a bit of hope,

637
00:35:56,840 --> 00:35:58,640
I won’t give up.

638
00:36:04,480 --> 00:36:08,180
♪Stars flow like river♪

639
00:36:09,010 --> 00:36:12,880
♪My yearning falls into the river♪

640
00:36:13,530 --> 00:36:17,440
♪I dare not ask if you’re doing well♪

641
00:36:17,890 --> 00:36:21,620
♪The first time I’ve felt terrified♪

642
00:36:22,700 --> 00:36:26,770
♪Youth is like a sweet dream♪

643
00:36:27,140 --> 00:36:30,900
♪The hope in heart never fades♪

644
00:36:31,770 --> 00:36:35,950
♪Now that you’re in my life♪

645
00:36:36,200 --> 00:36:39,770
♪I will never be alone♪

646
00:36:39,770 --> 00:36:44,240
♪I haven’t seen the mountains with you♪

647
00:36:44,240 --> 00:36:48,700
♪Nor have I tied up your hair♪

648
00:36:49,330 --> 00:36:54,110
♪We haven’t finished our story in chaos♪

649
00:36:54,110 --> 00:36:58,720
♪The blade hasn’t been returned♪

650
00:36:58,980 --> 00:37:02,930
♪I fear not to roam the world with you♪

651
00:37:02,930 --> 00:37:07,770
♪When I go across the world for you♪

652
00:37:07,920 --> 00:37:11,870
♪I’m willing to shed blood for you♪

653
00:37:12,030 --> 00:37:17,120
♪Don’t mind whose land it is♪

654
00:37:17,120 --> 00:37:21,080
♪Where is home to the snowflake♪

655
00:37:21,080 --> 00:37:25,540
♪Come and melt in my embrace♪

656
00:37:26,560 --> 00:37:28,080
I made you a small gift.

657
00:37:28,080 --> 00:37:33,640
♪The spring sun is an invisible armor
that’ll hold♪

658
00:37:33,990 --> 00:37:38,370
♪The purest love is unadorned♪

659
00:37:40,800 --> 00:37:41,560
Fei.

660
00:37:45,230 --> 00:37:46,710
I miss you so much.

661
00:38:06,800 --> 00:38:08,160
Girl.

662
00:38:10,430 --> 00:38:12,640
Why hasn’t Abbot Tongming come back yet?

663
00:38:14,400 --> 00:38:16,710
Do you think it’s so easy
to collect the herbs?

664
00:38:18,640 --> 00:38:20,840
I just fear Xie Yun can’t hold on.

665
00:38:21,230 --> 00:38:22,430
Don’t worry.

666
00:38:22,430 --> 00:38:25,400
Xie Yun will not die for the moment.

667
00:38:28,270 --> 00:38:29,840
This is for you.

668
00:38:31,190 --> 00:38:32,750
What is it?

669
00:38:44,840 --> 00:38:46,840
Looks so much like the Muyun Gauze

670
00:38:46,840 --> 00:38:49,120
Yin Pei was wearing.

671
00:38:49,120 --> 00:38:51,400
That’s rubbish.

672
00:38:51,400 --> 00:38:53,800
But this isn’t very precious, either.

673
00:38:53,800 --> 00:38:55,080
When I made the fishing net,

674
00:38:55,080 --> 00:38:57,320
there was some scrap material.

675
00:38:57,320 --> 00:39:00,030
It’s too small for others.

676
00:39:00,030 --> 00:39:02,270
But it just fits you.

677
00:39:03,670 --> 00:39:04,950
Girl.

678
00:39:04,950 --> 00:39:07,230
I’ve named it Rosy Cloud.

679
00:39:07,230 --> 00:39:09,640
What do you think?

680
00:39:12,640 --> 00:39:14,430
What are you laughing at?

681
00:39:15,560 --> 00:39:16,800
I’m laughing

682
00:39:16,800 --> 00:39:19,160
because it’s such a good name.

683
00:39:19,160 --> 00:39:21,160
Sounds glorified.

684
00:39:21,160 --> 00:39:22,160
Do you want it?

685
00:39:22,160 --> 00:39:22,990
If you don’t, give it back to me.

686
00:39:22,990 --> 00:39:25,670
I want it. It’s your gift for me.

687
00:39:27,710 --> 00:39:29,430
-You girl...
-Thank you.

688
00:39:36,640 --> 00:39:38,230
(Liang’s Mansion)
We’re terribly sorry.

689
00:39:38,230 --> 00:39:40,560
Our chief isn’t in lately.

690
00:39:40,560 --> 00:39:42,800
Where...? Where has he gone?

691
00:39:42,800 --> 00:39:45,120
We’re not sure.

692
00:39:53,470 --> 00:39:54,510
In a few days,

693
00:39:54,510 --> 00:39:56,560
it will be the birthday
of Lord Liu’s mother.

694
00:39:56,560 --> 00:39:57,470
Did he invite you?

695
00:39:57,470 --> 00:39:59,710
He did. But I’m not going.

696
00:39:59,710 --> 00:40:01,160
(Tea)
When Lord Liu invited you,

697
00:40:01,160 --> 00:40:02,670
it was your great honor.

698
00:40:04,560 --> 00:40:05,880
You don’t understand.

699
00:40:05,880 --> 00:40:08,190
A friend of mine works at Liu’s Manor.

700
00:40:08,190 --> 00:40:09,800
He told me

701
00:40:09,800 --> 00:40:11,990
Qinghui asked Lord Liu for money

702
00:40:11,990 --> 00:40:13,560
the other day.

703
00:40:13,560 --> 00:40:14,560
Unexpectedly,

704
00:40:14,560 --> 00:40:16,950
Lord Liu didn’t respect him at all.

705
00:40:16,950 --> 00:40:17,670
I’m afraid

706
00:40:17,670 --> 00:40:19,710
if we meet Qinghui that day,

707
00:40:19,710 --> 00:40:21,560
we’ll suffer.

708
00:40:21,560 --> 00:40:22,600
You’re right.

709
00:40:22,840 --> 00:40:24,030
(Lord Liu)
Mr. Liu.

710
00:40:24,400 --> 00:40:27,190
I asked nearby martial artists.

711
00:40:27,190 --> 00:40:28,670
No one wants to help us

712
00:40:28,670 --> 00:40:31,880
deal with Qinghui,

713
00:40:31,880 --> 00:40:33,510
We have few men.

714
00:40:33,510 --> 00:40:35,400
I’m afraid we can’t kill him.

715
00:40:35,400 --> 00:40:38,880
Since we’ve decided to kill him,

716
00:40:38,880 --> 00:40:40,710
we must do it,

717
00:40:40,710 --> 00:40:42,840
no matter how many men we have.

718
00:40:42,840 --> 00:40:44,990
Look at the martial world.

719
00:40:44,990 --> 00:40:47,320
Huo’s Manor is ruined.

720
00:40:47,320 --> 00:40:49,030
Yin Wenlan is dead.

721
00:40:49,030 --> 00:40:51,510
Qi School has disappeared.

722
00:40:51,800 --> 00:40:53,840
Even people
with the Fortress of the Forty-Eight

723
00:40:53,840 --> 00:40:56,230
are busy fighting against the Demons!

724
00:40:56,230 --> 00:40:59,640
If we can’t unite as one,

725
00:40:59,640 --> 00:41:02,400
how can we kill Qinghui?

726
00:41:03,560 --> 00:41:06,430
A lot of people are enemies of Qinghui!

727
00:41:06,430 --> 00:41:08,270
As long as we unite,

728
00:41:08,270 --> 00:41:09,990
we will kill him.

729
00:41:09,990 --> 00:41:11,640
Good point!

730
00:41:15,190 --> 00:41:15,840
Master.

731
00:41:15,840 --> 00:41:17,190
A Mr. Li asked to see you out there.

732
00:41:17,190 --> 00:41:19,470
He said he was Li Sheng
with the Fortress of the Forty-Eight.

733
00:41:19,470 --> 00:41:20,750
Li Sheng?

734
00:41:20,750 --> 00:41:23,080
Grandson of Li Zheng?

735
00:41:26,990 --> 00:41:28,800
I’m Li Sheng
with the Fortress of the Forty-Eight.

736
00:41:28,800 --> 00:41:32,920
Greetings, everyone.

737
00:41:33,750 --> 00:41:37,600
Mr. Li, what brings you here?

738
00:41:37,600 --> 00:41:39,750
I come here,

739
00:41:39,750 --> 00:41:41,640
for Qinghui.

740
00:41:42,990 --> 00:41:44,600
Qinghui?

741
00:41:47,510 --> 00:41:49,030
Lord Liu, you must know

742
00:41:49,030 --> 00:41:51,400
what Qinghui has done.

743
00:41:51,400 --> 00:41:52,710
The longer he lives,

744
00:41:52,710 --> 00:41:55,080
the more people will suffer.

745
00:41:55,080 --> 00:41:57,880
I want to unite everyone

746
00:41:57,880 --> 00:42:01,030
to kill him once for all.

747
00:42:01,470 --> 00:42:04,600
What’s your plan, Mr. Li?

748
00:42:04,600 --> 00:42:07,400
I’ve got a plan.

749
00:42:08,360 --> 00:42:12,560
To be honest, we do want to kill him.

750
00:42:12,560 --> 00:42:14,270
But we’re worried

751
00:42:14,270 --> 00:42:17,360
if we have enough men.

752
00:42:18,190 --> 00:42:20,670
I’ve travelled around, asking for help.

753
00:42:20,670 --> 00:42:21,800
I didn’t get as much support
as I expected.

754
00:42:21,800 --> 00:42:25,510
But still a lot of martial masters
are willing to help.

755
00:42:25,950 --> 00:42:27,510
Today, I come to you.

756
00:42:27,510 --> 00:42:28,560
If we can cooperate,

757
00:42:28,560 --> 00:42:30,670
we’ll stand a big chance.

758
00:42:31,950 --> 00:42:34,640
I’d like to set a trap in a few days.

759
00:42:34,640 --> 00:42:37,670
As for the place...

760
00:42:39,080 --> 00:42:42,640
Your yard looks good.

761
00:42:43,600 --> 00:42:45,560
As long as we can kill Qinghui,

762
00:42:45,560 --> 00:42:47,710
I won’t care for a mere yard!

763
00:42:49,640 --> 00:42:50,800
Good!

764
00:42:58,400 --> 00:43:00,160
Fei didn’t come?

765
00:43:00,880 --> 00:43:03,030
Miss Zhou Fei arrived yesterday.

766
00:43:03,030 --> 00:43:04,840
She was wandering around this morning.

767
00:43:04,840 --> 00:43:06,030
I don’t know

768
00:43:06,030 --> 00:43:08,270
where she is now.

769
00:43:08,270 --> 00:43:11,950
I had thought she wouldn’t stay

770
00:43:11,950 --> 00:43:14,360
and I would miss her
when I went for the herbs.

771
00:43:14,360 --> 00:43:15,990
She probably knows

772
00:43:15,990 --> 00:43:19,840
Xie Yun is getting weaker and weaker

773
00:43:19,840 --> 00:43:21,880
and she won’t see him for many times.

774
00:43:22,510 --> 00:43:25,230
She’s stayed for a few more days.

775
00:43:25,750 --> 00:43:27,270
I put the thing she brought

776
00:43:27,270 --> 00:43:29,600
on your bedside.

777
00:43:29,600 --> 00:43:31,130
It’s the Flaming Sage.

778
00:43:33,360 --> 00:43:36,580
She must have suffered a lot

779
00:43:37,360 --> 00:43:40,160
to collect these things.

780
00:43:53,990 --> 00:43:55,880
You’re lucky enough.

781
00:43:55,880 --> 00:43:57,150
I’ll let you go

782
00:43:57,710 --> 00:44:00,920
to pray for Xie Yun.

783
00:44:28,510 --> 00:44:30,990
I feel he’s waking up.

784
00:44:30,990 --> 00:44:32,470
How long has he been asleep?

785
00:44:32,470 --> 00:44:33,320
It’s about time.

786
00:44:33,320 --> 00:44:34,920
Yeah. Yeah.

787
00:44:38,990 --> 00:44:41,430
Anzhi, you’re awake?

788
00:44:41,430 --> 00:44:42,670
Junior Master.

789
00:44:42,920 --> 00:44:43,800
Come on.

790
00:44:44,670 --> 00:44:47,320
Be careful. Slow down.

791
00:44:47,800 --> 00:44:49,560
Get up slowly.

792
00:44:50,560 --> 00:44:53,560
Anzhi, I guess you’re waking up.

793
00:44:54,990 --> 00:44:55,990
Master.

794
00:44:55,990 --> 00:44:58,080
Come on. Take the decoction.

795
00:45:03,190 --> 00:45:04,430
Oh,

796
00:45:04,990 --> 00:45:06,800
how long were I asleep?

797
00:45:06,800 --> 00:45:08,320
Not very long.

798
00:45:11,190 --> 00:45:12,560
Where’s Fei?

799
00:45:13,120 --> 00:45:15,510
You really are a couple.

800
00:45:15,510 --> 00:45:17,400
No wonder you like each other.

801
00:45:17,400 --> 00:45:19,470
When you woke up, she fell asleep.

802
00:45:19,710 --> 00:45:21,080
She’s next door.

803
00:45:21,320 --> 00:45:24,230
Come on. Take it when it’s hot.

804
00:45:43,410 --> 00:45:46,930
♪Stars flow like river♪

805
00:45:47,970 --> 00:45:51,570
♪My yearning falls into the river♪

806
00:45:52,130 --> 00:45:56,210
♪Now that you’re in my life♪

807
00:45:56,450 --> 00:46:00,090
♪I will never be alone♪

808
00:46:00,090 --> 00:46:04,210
♪I haven’t seen the mountains with you♪

809
00:46:04,650 --> 00:46:09,090
♪Nor have I tied up your hair♪

810
00:46:09,730 --> 00:46:14,290
♪We haven’t finished our story in chaos♪

811
00:46:14,530 --> 00:46:19,170
♪The blade hasn’t been returned♪

812
00:46:19,330 --> 00:46:23,170
♪I fear not to roam the world with you♪

813
00:46:23,410 --> 00:46:28,090
♪When I go across the world for you♪

814
00:46:28,330 --> 00:46:32,090
♪I’m willing to shed blood for you♪

815
00:46:32,410 --> 00:46:37,490
♪Don’t mind whose land it is♪

816
00:46:37,490 --> 00:46:41,450
♪Where is home to the snowflake♪

817
00:46:41,450 --> 00:46:45,970
♪Come and melt in my embrace♪

818
00:46:46,610 --> 00:46:53,690
♪The spring sun is an invisible armor
that’ll hold♪

819
00:46:54,450 --> 00:46:59,050
♪The purest love is unadorned♪
